--- !u!114 &1281516622
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1281516616}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9afbba6bfbcaef74588ce683a94dbeb3, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPC_Butcher
  CanInteract: 1
  MyLines:
  - Line: "Good mornin\u2019 sunshine. You awright? Beeeyu-iful day we\u2019re avvin.
      Bit warm. Could do wiv somefin refreshin\u2026 "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Anyways, wot can I get ya? I got some lamb pie I made earlier that\u2019s
      bloody good. I\u2019ll do ya a deal if ya like.  "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "O-oh\u2026 that\u2019s nice. She\u2019s nice, aint she? Good lady. Siiiiiip.
      Oh, mango too. My favourite. I actually made an extra special pie, I wanted
      to give it to her but\u2026 "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "I\u2019m a bit shy. She sold me some lovely potatoes the uvva day, I put
      em in \u2018ere. I wonder if\u2026 Nah. I mean, if you\u2019d be willin\u2019,
      could you get this to her?  "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Wait, are you pulling my leg?? For real?? That\u2019s\u2026 bloody nora\u2026
      I need to get this pie to her asap! I already wrote a note to go wiv it. I\u2019m
      right sentimental when I want to be.  "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Don\u2019t read it! Thank you, mate. I really appreciate it. She\u2019s
      such a sweetie. "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Jovially, boisterously Really mate? You\u2019d be doin\u2019 me a proper
      solid, absolute legend! Here ya go, I wrapped it up special for her.  "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "No worries pal, I\u2019ll\u2026 I\u2019ll get it to her myself after work.
      Phew. Bit nervous to be honest. You\u2019re calming me down a bit though. Here,
      take a pie on the house.  "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Bloody hell, wot\u2019s that little bugger done now? I know I\u2019m not
      \u2018round all the time, bein a single mom an\u2019 all, but I wish he\u2019d
      be a little bit more considerate.   "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Runnin\u2019 with those other two does him no good, always trying to prove
      himself. Did you say anyfin\u2019?"
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Sigh Fanks. So embarrassin\u2019. I\u2019ll tryn\u2019 do better. I jus\u2019
      want my kid to be good, yanno? Have a good influence. I fink they\u2019re \u2018angin
      round the fruit vendor a lot. Maybe she\u2019ll be a good influence. "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  - Line: "Sigh Fanks. It\u2019s important for him to \u2018ear it from me, I oughtta
      be more present so he can learn to be a good boy. Luckily I think they hang
      out near the fruit vendor. I hope she rubs off on them\u2026 "
    Terminator: 0
    Choises: []
  ID: 14
